      <title>沙特阿拉伯的联想交易展示了现金换投资战略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/saudi-arabia-s-lenovo-deal-showcases-cash-for-investments-strategy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯将向联想集团有限公司投资 20 亿美元，这是该国利用现金储备吸引外国公司进入该国的最新举措，将支持该国政府摆脱对石油依赖、实现经济多元化的举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/saudi-arabia-s-lenovo-deal-showcases-cash-for-investments-strategy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 10:01:58 GMT</pubDate>
